@{
    var tenants = ViewData["Tenants"] as IEnumerable<TenantSite>;
}

<h1>
    SharePoint Embedded Demo
</h1>
<p>
    The purpose if this sample app is to exercise the Graph API that interact with Containers.

    As such, it presents data that wouldn't be needed for a typical user, especially IDs.
</p>


In order to use use this app:
<ul>
    <li>(Only once per new tenant). Onboard your tenant. Requires Admin privileges. This should add your tenant to the list of tenants.</li>
    <li>Select your tenant from the main screen and provide your credentials</li>
    <li>Proceed to create containers and interact with them.</li>
</ul>


<h2>Onboarded tenants:</h2>
<ul>

    @foreach (TenantSite tenant in tenants)
    {
        <li><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Containers" asp-action="Index" asp-route-tenantId="@tenant.TenantId">@tenant.Name</a></li>
    }
</ul>
<a class="btn btn-primary" asp-area="" asp-controller="Onboarding" asp-action="SignUp">Sign a tenant</a>



